Titolo: DrawRace 2

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: DrawRace 2 is a racing video game developed by RedLynx and published by Chillingo. It was released September 1, 2011 for iOS devices, and serves as the sequel to DrawRace. It is played by drawing an ideal racing line on the game's screen with a finger. The car then follows this line during a race. The game was well received by critics, and holds a four stars rating and an average score of 88/100 at review aggregator Metacritic.